# Build context exclusion list for the preview-site Fly image.
#
# Anything matched here is skipped before the Docker daemon snapshots
# the build context, which keeps `docker build` snappy and avoids
# accidentally shipping local-only artefacts (caches, IDE config,
# uncommitted git data) into the image.

# pnpm + node tooling outputs
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store
**/.turbo

# Vite / tsup outputs (rebuilt inside the container)
**/dist
**/dist-server
**/.vite
**/.preview-cache

# Test / coverage / lint outputs
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Editor / OS noise
.idea
.vscode
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Git internals — Docker doesn't need them and they bloat the context.
.git
.gitignore

# Claude session scratch
.claude
.claude-tasks
